{"tid":486131,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[畫畫JJ]想組一個晝力&創作力提升小組","createTime":"2017-12-01T14:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T06:48:57.000Z","uid":36673,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fed21bc344d8898f37dd3d581c52343596f3ac98","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打CD-RM大家好～<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，其實網絡上面都有唔少繪畫相關既group，自己都有join過唔少，但總覺得差咁D野：就係缺少左互相評價，同埋對於創作/創意既討論。<br />\n<br />\n好多時候只係得簡短既稱讚，最多係會講下有邊到畫錯左（透視、人體），但對於創作力（構成、構圖）之類既建議同評論都好缺乏。<br />\n當然可能因為係大家都在唔太敢評論，一來係驚講錯，一來係自覺自己仲未太夠班。<br />\n但呢樣風氣對創作並唔係太好，創作者係無feedback既情況下好難明自己做得好同做得差既地方（雖然繪畫已經算好直觀⋯）<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於此，所以構思緊成立一個可以只得5-8個既細group，定期有題目進行創作，唔係只係畫，而係討論埋構圖、題材、風格<br />\n之後大家進行討論，可以係記名，又可以用匿名，comment番每一張作品，令到作品唔會只係post左出黎，比人讚句幾靚就無人理咁。<br />\n<br />\n而呢一個group，甚至可以唔單止停留係網絡上面，而係可以係現實都交流，例如一齊睇展覽、開茶繪/讀書會等等。<br />\n希望香港有志於繪畫創作既人聚埋一齊，互相交流，互相進步。<br />\n<br />\n暫定只限電繪，但類型風格不限，年紀不限。唔一定需要畫得好好（本人都只係廢jer一條），但必須要抽時間積極參與繪畫活動同討論。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既可以填呢個Google form（<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/gtQHfrHShXj3aoPz1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FgtQHfrHShXj3aoPz1&d=HTedh34LeZNXxd3utFTRGS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0440986f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/gtQHfrHShXj3aoPz1</a>），比我了解下大家既意向，再遂個人聯絡。<br />\n如果人太多（雖然應該唔會），出現揀人既情況既話，我保證一定會解釋點解入唔到，同比番D建議&amp;有用資料比你～<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家 m(_ _)m"},{"pid":"6cc9089465e2608b75f7962c70a6f42facc9b2b4","tid":486131,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae67c1f635178e0a630d215cfc681b635dcc31c1","tid":486131,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de11f72ae61b789f02f032e54408ebccc5b1666e","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"竟然係肥絲幫我推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"89c0c87ac9f02b025f4a3b919b0b0c4d364ceb09","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1b86ff34bb54e10f49404a70f0a9ff2a618fbc","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"推～<br />\n填完唔介意既幫忙推下／比個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00d0665e0067b7037d5e873351cdb1c8667912c","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"訓前一推～"},{"pid":"898064885b4b84e9e14624a78b89ad1ffe2ee5d3","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7b6b0148d1ff8a018bded4f7f1a9fa437096ae","tid":486131,"uid":151740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:38:36.000Z","msg":"有畫開野但冇特別喜好邊個畫師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f53843a4cfe4e7e3734324dd23d4bc0252b8906","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有畫開野但冇特別喜好邊個畫師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係個ref for我/之後group既其他人了解下你~<br />\n喜好既風格唔同方向都會有唔同<br />\n例如萌系同歐美系已經係兩個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e47c04f51652e99183a5191da5b93c47d8d8bdf","tid":486131,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2b6bb75114d602e293192f5aad8079c63d7971","tid":486131,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:55:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ecd39bbe41955896aa